  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nWhen joining chat with messages for the first time (confirmed in public chat and 1-1 chat) the message replies starting to blinking each 5 seconds and whole list of messages redrawing too  \r\nWhen re-navigating to that chat, then only username blinks only once in reply snipped. \r\n\r\n**NOTE:**  In a case of above scenario when the message which was replied to is visible (like the reply is the very next message) then no issues\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nNo message blinking when the joinning the chat for the first time\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nEach 5 seconds after joining the chat with reply this what happens:\r\n\r\n![112121212](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/78782143-34797e00-79aa-11ea-8485-c6d3b6c60843.gif)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status and create new account\r\n- Join public chat where offline inboxed history exists\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: develop and release 1.2.0\r\n- Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nThese are logcat logs for what happens when blinking happens:\r\n\r\n```\r\n04-08 15:09:39.940  3150  3227 D ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.utils.handlers:32] - Handling re-frame event:  :chat.ui/message-visibility-changed\r\n04-08 15:09:40.173  3150  3227 D ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.utils.handlers:32] - Handling re-frame event:  :chat.ui/load-more-messages\r\n04-08 15:09:40.216  3150  3227 D ReactNativeJS: DEBUG [status-im.utils.handlers:32] - Handling re-frame event:  :status-im.chat.models.loading/messages-loaded\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n",
